HEADWORD: Potgun
<hw>Pot"gun`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A
pot-shaped cannon; a mortar.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> ⟦ldquo⟧Twelve
<xex>potguns</xex> of brass.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Hakluyt.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A popgun.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Swift.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pothecary</ent>⟦br⟧
